<p><em><strong>More on Lunar XPRIZE: <a href="https://futurism.com/googles-lunar-xprize-over-spaceflight-innovation/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google’s Lunar XPrize Is Over. Spaceflight Innovation, However, Is Not.</a></strong></em></p>
