<p><em><strong>More on radio jets: <a href="https://futurism.com/researchers-discover-bizarre-black-holes-aligned/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Researchers Discover “Bizarre” Black Holes That Are All Aligned</a></strong></em></p>
